snippet: Gunmen in the southern Iraqi desert near the border with Saudi Arabia overwhelmed a tent encampment and kidnapped at least 26 members of an expedition.

byline.original: By OMAR AL-JAWOSHY and RICK GLADSTONE
byline.contributor: Omar Al-Jawoshy reported from Baghdad, and Rick Gladstone from New York.

lead_paragraph: Gunmen in the southern Iraqi desert near the border with Saudi Arabia overwhelmed a tent encampment and kidnapped at least 26 members of an expedition.

headline.main: Qatari Safari Members, Including Royalty, Are Abducted in Iraq
